  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Willy West is a western top-down shoot 'em up, featuring action packed levels and instant death combat. Use an arsenal of magical bullets to blast your way through the old west, and take revenge on those who wronged you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ee791ef5d06dee32df7b7f6f791c5b5c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and upgrade a wide selection of unique magical bullets in order to take down your foes. You can only load six magic bullets into your gun at the start of a level, so use them carefully. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/01fc00756ea62ca3b119cd504e1c6d4c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter fearsome foes and terrifying bosses in a series of high action, hand crafted levels. Different enemies will require different approaches, forcing you to use your arsenal to it's fullest potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/bacaad4f190a669e3fe0738f4b338eee.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow William Wilde on his quest for revenge against the gang that ruined his life whilst unravelling the mystery of Willy's new mysterious companion, the witch.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Willy West is a western top-down shoot 'em up, featuring action packed levels and instant death combat. Use an arsenal of magical bullets to blast your way through the old west, and take revenge on those who wronged you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ee791ef5d06dee32df7b7f6f791c5b5c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and upgrade a wide selection of unique magical bullets in order to take down your foes. You can only load six magic bullets into your gun at the start of a level, so use them carefully. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/01fc00756ea62ca3b119cd504e1c6d4c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter fearsome foes and terrifying bosses in a series of high action, hand crafted levels. Different enemies will require different approaches, forcing you to use your arsenal to it's fullest potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/bacaad4f190a669e3fe0738f4b338eee.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/141567c2550418ecbdeb82eb2dfc4b6b.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow William Wilde on his quest for revenge against the gang that ruined his life whilst unravelling the mystery of Willy's new mysterious companion, the witch.</p>",
